Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}音速より速く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}嵐も切り裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:54.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}魔法の翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}守りたい　君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}辛くて　泣きそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}時も　そばにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:06.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ぜったい　譲れない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}青い青い　この場所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}さあ　飛ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あふれだす勇気　盾に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}羽ばたいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:24.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}迫る闇　全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}振り切ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:30.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}昨日より強い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.39,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}私になれ
