Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:38.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}光芒照射的另一端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}用手遮起來看過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}從指間縫隙裡看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}是那天立下誓約的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}超越音速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}切開暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:54.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}用魔法的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}來守護你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即使在痛苦想要哭泣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我也在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:06.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那片湛藍湛藍的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}絕不讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}來  一起飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}將噴薄而出的勇氣化作盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:24.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}把襲來的黑暗全都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}一掃而光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:30.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}要變得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}比昨天的我更強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:40.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}現在  就向著那閃耀的天空而去
