Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安恆之星
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.39,0:25:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳和麗奈大顯身手？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.86,0:25:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
